  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You belch a massive gout of flame towards your enemies. Creatures in the area of effect take 8d6 fire damage and must make a Reflex save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and @Damage[(1+(@item.level -4))[persistent,fire]] damage.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and @Damage[(1+(@item.level -4))d6[persistent,fire]] damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d6, the persistent damage on a failure increases by 1, and the persistent damage on a critical failure increases by 1d6.</p>"
